
List sites for a shipper.

See: https://google.aip.dev/132 (Standard methods: List).

USAGE
  list-sites <command>

ARGUMENT FLAGS
  --parent      [R]  string  Resource name of the parent, which owns this collection of sites
  --page-size        int32   Requested page size
  --page-token       string  A token identifying a page of results the server should return
  --skip             int32   Number of resource to skip in the request

CONNECTION FLAGS
  --address        string  Connect to address
  --force-trace    bool    Enable forced Google Cloud Trace header
  --insecure       bool    Make insecure connection (only on localhost)
  --token          string  Authenticate with a bearer token

OTHER FLAGS
  -f  --from-file    string  path to a JSON file containing the request payload
  -h  --help         bool    Show help for command
  -v  --verbose      bool    Enable verbose output
